  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Turning Of Heaven
---
\"Have you never seen a well sweep? Pull it, and down it comes; let go,
and up it swings. It allows itself to be pulled around by men; it
doesn't try to pull them. So it can go up and down and never get blamed
by anybody.
